OL,3,CThe backlash and fallout the
OL,4,CBirmingham Pub Bombings had on Irish
OL,5,CBrummies
OL,7,FITV Central Reporter Ravneet Nandra
OL,8,Fspoke with those who's lives changed
OL,9,Fforever after the Birmingham Pub
OL,10,FBombings
OL,12,FMaurice Malone was just seven years
OL,13,Fold when the bombs exploded at two
OL,14,Fpubs in Birmingham city centre in 1974.
OL,16,FHe said he felt the impact of that
OL,17,Fnight almost instantly. His mother was
OL,18,Fscared of him walking to school alone
OL,19,Fthe day after, and took him instead.
