OL,3,CThe backlash and fallout the
OL,4,CBirmingham Pub Bombings had on Irish
OL,5,CBrummies
OL,7,F'We and the Irish community had become
OL,8,Fa suspect community, treated as
OL,9,Fterrorists in the city'
OL,11,FBombs exploded in the Mulberry Bush
OL,12,Fand the Tavern in the Town pubs
OL,13,Fkilling 21 and injuring almost 200
OL,14,Fothers.
OL,16,FSix people, called the Birmingham Six,
OL,17,Fwere jailed for the murders, but were
OL,18,Fexonerated and freed 17 years later.
OL,19,FIt remains Britain's biggest unsolved
OL,20,Fmass murder.
