OL,3,CThe backlash and fallout the
OL,4,CBirmingham Pub Bombings had on Irish
OL,5,CBrummies
OL,7,FThe IRA is thought to have been
OL,8,Fresponsible, despite never claiming
OL,9,Fresponsibility.
OL,11,FMaurice believed things changed for
OL,12,Fthe Irish community overnight. He said
OL,13,Fhe woke up the following morning and
OL,14,Fhis world changed.
OL,16,FHe said: "It transpired dad had gone
OL,17,Finto the factory Friday morning which
OL,18,Fwas the day after the bombings, and
OL,19,Fhe'd been attacked by people who he'd
OL,20,Fwork along side for years and years,
OL,21,Fpeople he classed as his friends.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
