OL,3,CThe backlash and fallout the
OL,4,CBirmingham Pub Bombings had on Irish
OL,5,CBrummies
OL,7,F"They turned on him and he got a few
OL,8,Fbeatings at work. And him and other
OL,9,Ffellows who were Irish were told to
OL,10,Fleave to leave the factory for their
OL,11,Fown safety.
OL,13,F"That was code for: your jobs gone,
OL,14,Fyou're not coming back to work here
OL,15,Fagain.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
