OL,3,CThe backlash and fallout the
OL,4,CBirmingham Pub Bombings had on Irish
OL,5,CBrummies
OL,7,F"I've always said my dad died that
OL,8,Fnight as well but he didn't realise
OL,9,Fand he didn't find out till years
OL,10,Flater because it broke him, it broke
OL,11,Four family. He dealt with it the only
OL,12,Fway he thought he could and he turned
OL,13,Fto drink.
OL,15,F"His life spiralled downwards from
OL,16,Fthere. He moved back to Ireland and
OL,17,Fleft myself and my mum.
OL,19,F"We and the Irish community had become
OL,20,Fa suspect community, treated as
OL,21,Fterrorists in the city."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
