OL,3,CThe backlash and fallout the
OL,4,CBirmingham Pub Bombings had on Irish
OL,5,CBrummies
OL,7,F"And all of a sudden he was taken
OL,8,Faway, so, I think it certainly shaped
OL,9,Fhow my life turned out and I would
OL,10,Fimagine for a lot of lives in the
OL,11,FIrish community and I think if that
OL,12,Fwouldn't have happened, things would
OL,13,Fhave been very different for a lot of
OL,14,Fpeople."
OL,16,FA government spokesperson said: "Our
OL,17,Fdeepest sympathies remain with all
OL,18,Fthose who continue to be affected by
OL,19,Fthe horrific pub bombings in
OL,20,FBirmingham in 1974."
